<p><span class="Apple" style="margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 10px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; outline-width: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; padding: 0px;">Orders over $200 will automatically have signature required for the package. <br /></span></span></p>
